"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641181934,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"0W4EUHVndfhP2NO-nav-u5eGPVilGCyEKqIbghPz9j0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x7a9413b258330e52eFa8DD270Bc6cbE30DFb5641\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dmDoehlX9akA5-SpGO39JHR0wF0Gd5tgoCVYwTkLwYM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0hTm8zL154Xj8olsXPRtscbJPAICwTU7mehRGE_gRYg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"AmRyebEGP3VdN34FtxuM5DIbFRaopa6pcBzicxX2K6R7oT3cB7c5AZgsVHPM526Fb5ol9oeboejYLBZhZcvczg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb186e1e9011952f5c40ae974e5b4195022a31eaf1c0c79dbe55a5bc48116c14b34e629f158988fd7c0a5654c7f301319d4d128e867e2ada4ada478c99a5305381c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dmDoehlX9akA5-SpGO39JHR0wF0Gd5tgoCVYwTkLwYM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0hTm8zL154Xj8olsXPRtscbJPAICwTU7mehRGE_gRYg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi